'''Grendaju''' was an icy landmass at the southern extreme of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kalee/Legends|Kalee]].

It was believed that Grendaju was the last land where the [[Karabbac/Legends|karabbac]] were known to roam, and it was thought that [[Ronderu lij Kummar]] hailed from this area. [[Grievous/Legends|Qymaen jai Sheelal]] was once shipwrecked on Grendaju, during which time he found and recruited one of the khans of his ''[[Izvoshra/Legends|Izvoshra]]'' elite.

